document.masterDocTitle: An annotated list of the Acanthocephala from Argentina

mods:titleInfo.mods:title: An annotated list of the Acanthocephala from Argentina

subSubSection.paragraph:
Adenomera diptyx (Boettger)
( Anura , Leptodactylidae ). SI: mesenteries. SD: cystacanth. L: Formosa Province : Naick Neck Lagoon ( 25º10’S , 58º07’W ); Corrientes Province : Paso de la Patria ( 27º19’S , 58º46’W ), Corrientes City ( 27º28’S , 58º46’W ). R: Zaracho and Lamas (2008) ,
Zaracho et al. (2012)
. C: vouchers (MLP-He, accession numbers not provided).

Leptodactylus bufonius Boulenger
( Anura , Leptodactylidae ). SI: mesenteries, serosa of stomach. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27º30’S , 58º45’W ). R:
González et al. (2006a)
,
Hamann et al. (2012)
,
Campião et al. (2014)
. C: vouchers (CECOAL 10021703 ).

Leptodactylus chaquensis Cei
( Anura , Leptodactylidae ). SI: mesenteries, serosa of stomach. SD: cystacanth. L Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27º30’S , 58º45’W ), non-agricultural area in the northwestern part of Corrientes Province ( 27º27’S , 58º47’W ), agricultural area in the northwestern part of Corrientes Province ( 27º36’S , 58º48’W ). R:
Hamann et al. (2006b)
,
Schaefer et al. (2006)
. C: vouchers (CECOAL accession numbers not provided).

Leptodactylus latinasus Jiménez de la Espada
( Anura , Leptodactylidae ). SI: mesenteries. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : northwestern part of Corrientes Province ( 27º27’S , 58º47’W ). R:
Hamann et al. (2006a)
. C: vouchers ( CECOAL
03052908
)
.

Melanophryniscus klappenbachi Prigioni & Langone
( Anura , Bufonidae ). SI: serosa of stomach. SD: cystacanth. L: Chaco Province : Chaco biogeographic Province ( 27°23’S , 58°58’W ). R:
Hamann et al. (2014)
. C: vouchers ( CECOAL 12113009 )
.

Pseudopaludicola boliviana Parker
( Anura , Leptodactylidae ). SI: mesenteries. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27º30’S , 58º45’W ). R:
Duré et al. (2004)
.

Rhinella fernandezae (Gallardo)
( Anura , Bufonidae ). SI: serosa of stomach, mesenteries. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27°30’S , 58°45’W ). R:
Hamann et al. (2013)
. C: vouchers ( CECOAL 09020606 )
.

Scinax nasicus (Cope)
( Anura , Hylidae ). SI: liver, mesenteries, serosa of stomach. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27°30’S , 58°45’W ), Paraná River. R:
Hamann et al. (2009
, 2010 ). C: vouchers (CECOAL 04092904 , 06083118).

Aves
Athene cunicularia (Molina)
( Strigiformes , Strigidae ). SI: intestine. SD: juvenile. L: Formosa Province : Marcela farm ( 26°17’35’’S ; 59°08’38’’W ). R:
Drago et al. (2015)
. C: vouchers (MLP-He 7248).

Paraphimophis rusticus (Cope)
( Squamata , Dipsadidae ). SI: mesenteries (anterior part of intestine). SD: cystacanth. L: Buenos Aires Province : Villa Elisa. R: Vizcaíno (1993) .

Leptophis ahaetulla marginatus (Cope)
( Squamata , Colubridae ). SI: mesenteries. SD: cystacanth. L: Corrientes Province : Corrientes City ( 27º28’01’’S , 58º47’00’’W ). R: Lamas and Lunaschi (2009) . C: vouchers (MLP- He 5874).
